05:42.614 --> 05:46.277
<i>♪ See the money,</i>
<i>wanna stay for your meal ♪</i>

05:46.278 --> 05:49.579
<i>♪ Get another piece of pie</i>
<i>for your wife ♪</i>

05:49.615 --> 05:52.749
<i>♪ Everybody wanna know</i>
<i>how it feel ♪</i>

05:52.785 --> 05:56.520
<i>♪ Everybody wanna see</i>
<i>what it's like ♪</i>

05:56.555 --> 05:59.422
<i>♪ I'll even eat a bean pie,</i>
<i>I don't mind ♪</i>

05:59.458 --> 06:03.426
<i>♪ Me and Missy is</i>
<i>so busy, busy making money ♪</i>

06:03.462 --> 06:04.895
<i>♪ All right ♪</i>

06:04.930 --> 06:05.467
<i>♪ All step back,</i>
<i>I'm 'bout to dance ♪</i>

06:05.468 --> 06:10.468
